question: Show me duty-free shops and souvenir stores that are located at Terminal 3.
sql_query1:
SELECT RetailOutlets.Name 
FROM RetailOutlets
WHERE (RetailOutlets.type = "Duty-Free Shop" OR RetailOutlets.type = "Souvenir Store") AND RetailOutlets.location = "Terminal 3"
sql_query2:
SELECT RetailOutlets.Name 
FROM RetailOutlets
WHERE RetailOutlets.type = "Duty-Free Shop" OR RetailOutlets.type = "Souvenir Store" AND RetailOutlets.location = "Terminal 3"
interpretation1: Which duty-free shops are located at Terminal 3 and which souvenir stores are located at the same terminal?
interpretation2: Provide a list of all duty-free shops and also provide a list of souvenir stores that are located at Terminal 3.
